des:
Amazon Alexa and the TediSmart home products work together to help you control home appliance nice and easy.
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light. 
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 
After connecting Alexa to your TediSmart products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "TediSmart" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one TediSmart account in our "TediSmart" app;
(3). You need to have some TediSmart devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our “TediSmart” app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "TediSmart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "TediSmart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "TediSmart", and you'll be navigated to TediSmart login page;
(9). Input your TediSmart account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on kitchen light"
“Alexa, turn off kitchen light"
“Alexa, dim livingroom light"
“Alexa, brighten livingroom light"
“Alexa, set the livingroom light to 20 percent"
